  <div id="tutorweb_options" class="get_smly_section">
    <div class="get_smly_section_info_text">
      <h2> 2. Get SMLY by studying in the tutor-web system </h2>
      <p> The <a href="https://tutor-web.net/">tutor-web system</a> is a completely free and open system of study. You can pick any course or study-unit (tutorial) and study this to your hearts content by reading the available material and (most importantly) answering drill questions. As you increase your grade in those drills, you will get SMLY. Once you have SMLY you can download them into a Smileycoin wallet. </p>
    </div>
